Package co.edu.unbosque.view

package co.edu.unbosque.view
The package co.edu.unbosque.view host the classes related to the user interface of the system. It includes the main window and several panels that handle different parts of the GUI The classes in this package are: -MainWindow: represents the main window of the system. -MenuPanel: panel that contains buttons to navigate between functions. -RegistrationPanel: panel to register new elements in the system. -PersonListPanel: panel to display the list of registered items. -ListSortByAgePanel: panel to display the list sorted by age. This classes work together to provide an intuitive and functional graphical interface to the user.
